All indication - via bottom line (where is desktop indicator)

F2  - switch to console
F3  - 
F4  - h <--> c

# Indentations
F6  - toggle indentation between TABS and 4SPACES

F9  - toggle space-symbols displaying (enabled by default)
F10 - toggle row-numbers displaying (hide extra symbols), toggle space-symbols if enabled
